	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Search and save Linkwarden bookmarks.

## Setup
Set `LINKWARDEN_URL` and `LINKWARDEN_API_KEY` in the workflow variables.

## Usage
- `ln &lt;query&gt;` — Search bookmarks by name or tag. Press Enter to open, Ctrl+Enter for preserved version.
- `lna &lt;url&gt;` — Save a URL to Linkwarden.</string>
